Name: Collector
About the game: Are you ready for challenge? A fun and challenging game played at the click of a mouse. Try to collect golds in the levels with the fast-moving COLLECTOR. Here's the kind of game you've never played before; * There are two types of play styles: against time and with a certain number of moves. * 80+ Levels and 12 Challenges. * Play just one touch, It's so simple. * Compete with other players with the score table. * Just finish the sections or try to meet challenging goals. Maybe just play again to increase your score. PS. The game is not like the games you have played before. So please watch the gameplay video before you buy it.
